  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >THIS GAME IS EXTREMELY STRESSFUL, GOOD LUCK!</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2721690/extras/f7504cf05a0433293534325a8d15ae16.webp?t=1746394319\" width=616 height=42 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get frying and dive into  exhilarating kitchen shenanigans! Take control of a bustling Fish and Chip Shop and manage customers, unlock and cook tasty dishes, customise and grow your store and avoid pesky bills -<i> can you handle the stress?</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2721690/extras/dea7f6297b675d2c761f34506b9b8599.avif?t=1746394319\" width=616 height=192 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2721690/extras/62822b35e8e9fa54bb1ae940374f7384.webp?t=1746394319\" width=616 height=42 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An <i>impending invasion</i> threatens to end Fish and Chips throughout the nation. Work to defend the town of Scrumpton and your country from this terror.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bribe your customers to join the rebellion and assist them in defeating the incoming army by serving them with the dish you know best!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2721690/extras/980708e36c0e3e7a71aca92fdb54e357.avif?t=1746394319\" width=616 height=192 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2721690/extras/cac4119013b4bff7f2d6c64d02d8c2ce.webp?t=1746394319\" width=616 height=42 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Working together</i> is your key to success - Manage your chippy with friends and expand your empire together in servers of 1-5 people.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2721690/extras/9979189b7fe6f34c71753e7fca6635fb.avif?t=1746394319\" width=616 height=192 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2721690/extras/974a23395b41c6963423752738db73f3.webp?t=1746394319\" width=616 height=42 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Hungry customers</i> are swarming to your shop. Juggle cooking food, cleaning litter, stopping robbers and much more to keep them happy and improve your ratings!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2721690/extras/9ad203d0d70ac6fdb325a6a6365dee78.avif?t=1746394319\" width=616 height=192 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2721690/extras/311b27a2b36a0321b8e0293381bea10a.webp?t=1746394319\" width=616 height=42 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose from a catalogue of furniture, appliances, utilities and decorations to deck out your Chippy. Upgrade your chip shop and <i>create the ultimate seaside restaurant</i> - while cooking up a storm in the kitchen!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2721690/extras/1ae0a27084f1a937c98d1c72c7db586b.avif?t=1746394319\" width=616 height=192 /></span></p>",
